{
  "id": "67bce83a822f1c77adec7a72",
  "title": "一億人で議論できるシステム",
  "created": 1740433470,
  "updated": 1740464958,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "67bce83a822f1c77adec7a72",
      "text": "一億人で議論できるシステム",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740433470,
      "updated": 1740433470
    },
    {
      "id": "67bce83d71b3c200001585aa",
      "text": "[/blu3mo-public/「一億人で議論できるシステム」]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740433470,
      "updated": 1740433470
    },
    {
      "id": "67bce83d71b3c200001585ac",
      "text": "#一億人 #議論 #システム",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740433470,
      "updated": 1740433490
    },
    {
      "id": "67bce83d71b3c200001585ab",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740433470,
      "updated": 1740433710
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcead171b3c200001585b0",
      "text": "<think by=\"bsahd\">",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740434130,
      "updated": 1740435302
    },
    {
      "id": "67bceacf71b3c200001585ae",
      "text": " Step 1: [/blu3mo-public/多人数と議論する仕組み]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740434128,
      "updated": 1740434150
    },
    {
      "id": "67bceae771b3c200001585b1",
      "text": " 議論にループが発生している場合、それは不毛な議論",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740434151,
      "updated": 1740434194
    },
    {
      "id": "67bceb3271b3c200001585b2",
      "text": " AI間での議論内容の共有が重要",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740434227,
      "updated": 1740434236
    },
    {
      "id": "67bceb3c71b3c200001585b3",
      "text": " Step 2: [/blu3mo-public/103万の壁問題のヤフコメでmass-deliberation]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740434236,
      "updated": 1740434249
    },
    {
      "id": "67bceb5c71b3c200001585b5",
      "text": " 研究用のデータ置き場",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740434269,
      "updated": 1740434276
    },
    {
      "id": "67bceb6671b3c200001585b6",
      "text": " Step 3: [/blu3mo-public/世界の分断をなくすのではなく、世界の分断を100個作る]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740434278,
      "updated": 1740434284
    },
    {
      "id": "67bceb6c71b3c200001585b7",
      "text": " 分断が増えたほうが本質的に議論できる",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740434285,
      "updated": 1740434342
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcee1d71b3c200001585b9",
      "text": " 1つの大きな分断から100の小さな分断になる",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740434974,
      "updated": 1740434989
    },
    {
      "id": "67bceeaa71b3c200001585bf",
      "text": " それぞれの分断は二項対立",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435114,
      "updated": 1740435119
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcee2c71b3c200001585ba",
      "text": " これにより議論が円滑化する",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740434989,
      "updated": 1740434996
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcee4171b3c200001585bb",
      "text": " トランプ教とハリス教ではなく、人口中絶などの具体的な話題に対する対立",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435009,
      "updated": 1740435125
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcf21171b3c200001585d8",
      "text": " [/nishio/紙と箱の投票]では対立の数は必然的に限られていた",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435986,
      "updated": 1740436026
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcee6e71b3c200001585bc",
      "text": " [X.icon]対立ならいっぱいあるよ",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435055,
      "updated": 1740435062
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcee8b71b3c200001585be",
      "text": " 一億人で議論するというのと[エコーチェンバー内で学級会]するのとは違いそう",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435083,
      "updated": 1740464823
    },
    {
      "id": "67bceeb871b3c200001585c0",
      "text": " Step 4: [/blu3mo-public/対面コミュニケーションを機械にやらせる]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435128,
      "updated": 1740435176
    },
    {
      "id": "67bceee371b3c200001585c2",
      "text": "\tStep 5: [/blu3mo-public/medium-chat]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435171,
      "updated": 1740435184
    },
    {
      "id": "67bceef971b3c200001585c4",
      "text": "\tStep 6: [/blu3mo-public/大人数と議論する仕組み]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435193,
      "updated": 1740435209
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcef3c71b3c200001585c6",
      "text": "\tStep 7: [/blu3mo-public/大人数との議論を圧縮する仕組み]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435260,
      "updated": 1740435263
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcef3f71b3c200001585c7",
      "text": "\tStep 8: [/blu3mo-public/人間と機械、非同期と同期、主観と客観の間をなめらかにしたい]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435265,
      "updated": 1740435272
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcef4871b3c200001585c8",
      "text": "\tStep 9: [/blu3mo-public/人型実体]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435273,
      "updated": 1740435290
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcef8b71b3c200001585c9",
      "text": "\tStep 10: [/blu3mo-public/LLMと人間は環世界が違うだけ]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435340,
      "updated": 1740435342
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcef8e71b3c200001585ca",
      "text": "\tLLMが人間との対話を通じて世界のモデルを構築するのも良さそう",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435343,
      "updated": 1740435371
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcefab71b3c200001585cb",
      "text": "\tStep 11: [/blu3mo-public/考えるとはどういうことか]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435371,
      "updated": 1740435390
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcefbe71b3c200001585cc",
      "text": "\tStep 12: [/blu3mo-public/イシューからはじめよ]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435390,
      "updated": 1740435422
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd62fe71b3c200005cc32f",
      "text": "\t\t[/blu3mo-public/「シャワー浴びてから働き始めよう」でスタックする]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740464894,
      "updated": 1740464894
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd631071b3c200005cc333",
      "text": "\tタスクから始めることでスタックが減らせる",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740464913,
      "updated": 1740464913
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcf00f71b3c200001585ce",
      "text": "\tStep 13: [/blu3mo-public/コミュニケーションを支援する翻訳]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435471,
      "updated": 1740435504
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcf03071b3c200001585cf",
      "text": "\t映像翻訳とは?",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435504,
      "updated": 1740435565
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcf0ae71b3c200001585d2",
      "text": "\t\t画像内のテキストを検出しテキスト翻訳に渡す?",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435631,
      "updated": 1740435641
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcf07671b3c200001585d0",
      "text": "\t音声翻訳とは?",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435574,
      "updated": 1740435578
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcf07a71b3c200001585d1",
      "text": "\t\t私はマルチモーダルとかは使ったことないけど...",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435578,
      "updated": 1740435645
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcf0bd71b3c200001585d3",
      "text": "\t\t文字起こし、テキスト翻訳、音声合成の組み合わせと何が違うのか",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435645,
      "updated": 1740435763
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcf18771b3c200001585d5",
      "text": "\t\t[Cotomo]と[Advanced Voice mode]の違いがわからない",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435848,
      "updated": 1740436042
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcf19f71b3c200001585d6",
      "text": " \t\tどちらも文字起こし、LLM、音声合成の組み合わせでは",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740435872,
      "updated": 1740436045
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcebb771b3c200001585b8",
      "text": "</think>",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740434360,
      "updated": 1740435171
    },
    {
      "id": "67bcead071b3c200001585af",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740434128,
      "updated": 1740434128
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd19ce79e1130000c12b22",
      "text": "関連のある断片がちゃんと吸われていて感動[blu3mo.icon]",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1740446159,
      "updated": 1740446177
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd19e179e1130000c12b24",
      "text": "　aiにもこれくらいできるようになってほしい",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1740446177,
      "updated": 1740446201
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd54b7aff09e00005023d5",
      "text": "　Cosenseをたどりながら思考してるAI(または人)を眺めるのはそれ自体が面白い気がするな[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1740461240,
      "updated": 1740461340
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd551caff09e00005023d6",
      "text": "　 [memex]の「[連想の航跡]」だな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1740461340,
      "updated": 1740461381
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd19d479e1130000c12b23",
      "text": "\t自分も最近人力RAGみたいなのをやったりする[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1740446164,
      "updated": 1740462106
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd58196eb40600002aeaef",
      "text": "\t\tあるトピックを中心に関係ありそうなページを一旦集める",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1740462106,
      "updated": 1740462119
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd58356eb40600002aeaf1",
      "text": "\t\t\t本当はここはベクトル検索とかするところだけど、人力で集める",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1740462134,
      "updated": 1740462148
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd58276eb40600002aeaf0",
      "text": "\t\tそのページの中身を展開してLLMに食わせて質問する",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1740462119,
      "updated": 1740462132
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd633671b3c200005cc336",
      "text": "\t2 hop linksを辿ってるので当然ですが...[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1740464951,
      "updated": 1740464958
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd580a6eb40600002aeaee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1740462090,
      "updated": 1740462090
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd21da55cbd300005f551b",
      "text": "<think by=\"mtane0412\">",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1740448219,
      "updated": 1740448228
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd21e755cbd300005f551e",
      "text": " なんかすごい",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1740448231,
      "updated": 1740448233
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd21e455cbd300005f551d",
      "text": "</think>",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1740448228,
      "updated": 1740448230
    },
    {
      "id": "67bd21db55cbd300005f551c",
